    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/f7e1a72068e7ee0137a231c239d20f34.poster.avif?t=1681395021\" width=500 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/f7e1a72068e7ee0137a231c239d20f34.webm?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/f7e1a72068e7ee0137a231c239d20f34.mp4?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Slasher RPG</strong></h2>Fantasy Openworld style game, grow vegetables, crafting building and action adventures in a wide world.<br>Content mix : farming, pet breeding, dungeon exploration, crafting and combat. and the possibilities are endless. Along with stories and interesting things that are waiting for you to explore.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/a76332f5667b50e693eb4e6f8019dacb.poster.avif?t=1681395021\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/a76332f5667b50e693eb4e6f8019dacb.webm?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/a76332f5667b50e693eb4e6f8019dacb.mp4?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gathering</strong></h2>You can collect crops and build the garden of your dreams. And bring various raw materials to build.. Bring valuable products Let's get rich<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/d57d0dbc1171295f52f09c4a1916ac6b.poster.avif?t=1681395021\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/d57d0dbc1171295f52f09c4a1916ac6b.webm?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/d57d0dbc1171295f52f09c4a1916ac6b.mp4?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pet</strong></h2>Catch many kinds of animals in the game, raise and grow with these cute pets. There are many pets waiting for you to discover them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/12633c5fa65b31dd8319e19cd1c3ecea.poster.avif?t=1681395021\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/12633c5fa65b31dd8319e19cd1c3ecea.webm?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/12633c5fa65b31dd8319e19cd1c3ecea.mp4?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dungeon</strong></h2>The dungeon has many treasures and high-level materials and powerful monsters that are ready to kill you at any time. Please avoid them if you are not strong enough, many monsters are waiting for you<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/02dcdae8c6a4f09e964c5f2ccdbd133a.poster.avif?t=1681395021\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/02dcdae8c6a4f09e964c5f2ccdbd133a.webm?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196230/extras/02dcdae8c6a4f09e964c5f2ccdbd133a.mp4?t=1681395021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Vehicle</strong></h2>Find various mounts or vehicles and ride on adventures in the big world. There are many mounts or vehicles waiting for you to go on an adventure together!",
